{"about_the_game":"<i>You are the strongest, wisest and bravest of our tribe.<br>You must complete the trials to become Chief.<br>The trials lie ahead.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Classic Platforming - Classic Challenge</h2><br>Pacifist Outside is a cinematic platformer in the vein of games like the original Prince of Persia, Abe's Oddysee and Another World. It is every bit as uncompromising as its predecessors: failure is frequent and progress is hard-earned.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779810/extras/Screen1Small.png?t=1635701363\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Mystical Paths - Terrifying Truths</h2><br>Play as a brave tribal leader, grappling with strange trials and unknown forces, as he makes a spiritual journey through a dark cave. Dash through heart-pounding chases, solve devious puzzles and discover the secrets within the cave.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779810/extras/Screen2Small.png?t=1635701363\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Artistic Touch - Unique Presentation</h2><br>A carefully crafted experience, designed screen-by-screen, featuring a distinct art style and spanning 150 screens, each with painstakingly drawn unique backdrops. And all of this accompanied by nearly half an hour of ambient and otherworldly music by Shugendo - the journey is every bit as important as the destination.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Trials Lie Ahead</h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779810/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1635701363","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779810/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1635701363","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779810/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1635701363","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779810/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1635701